          "datePublished": "2016-04-17",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Right school for those who wish to join their KIDS in a good and best affordable school in CBSE curriculum in and around Chrompet, Pammal, Pallavaram, Thirumidivakkam, Thiruneermalai areas. I  joined my daughter in LKG after visited so many schools in Pammal area and finally my search ends in SSAV. Here are the positives of SSAV:\n- Finding  students raw talent and provide a platform  to showcase their talents.\n- Providing good and quality education.\n- Very care to their students.\n- Never gave any false commitments and never encouraging commercial gimmicks.\n- In this world of commercial world, this school is really a alternative.\n- Good environment for students to focus on their primary and secondary skills.\nFinally I have to say about the coordinator, Madam Rajaammal, President awardee. She is very kind to each and every students and she is an encouraging & motivating factor for all our parents like me.\n- Before join your kids in any school, please visit this school and finally decide your Kids future.  I am sure, this school will turn your kids to the right direction.\n\nAll the best.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
