            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The school has excellent infrastructure with state of the art lab facilities.\nThey conduct lot of activities to elevate the skills of the students.\nPersonal and individual care for every student.\nThe fee is nominal and in near future, this school will emerge as a center of excellence in all areas.\nThe management is very keen in conducting more activities.\nFrequent field trips are arranged for all the classes.\nThe faculty team is highly talented.",
